# Normalize text line endings (binary files left untouched). New/changed files
# are normalized to LF in the repo; checkout EOL is per-platform.
* text=auto

# Reference fixtures / blobs: never apply EOL or other munging. The cross-
# platform parity fixtures (e.g. the gcc-generated __int128 NTT oracle vectors)
# must be byte-identical on every platform.
*.bin   binary
*.gguf  binary
*.safetensors binary
